45
00:03:41,680 --> 00:03:43,800
Her movements are too stiff,

46
00:03:44,200 --> 00:03:45,200
like a machine.

47
00:03:48,200 --> 00:03:48,880
Also,

48
00:03:49,640 --> 00:03:53,100
