84
00:05:05,720 --> 00:05:08,050
We still need evidence to prove hypnosis.

85
00:05:08,280 --> 00:05:10,360
Whatever the cause of Liang Ruqing's death,

86
00:05:10,360 --> 00:05:12,040
we need to find evidence.

87
