117
00:06:01,320 --> 00:06:02,360
It's yours.

118
00:06:03,320 --> 00:06:04,000
All yours.

119
00:06:04,560 --> 00:06:05,520
Ms. Xu,

120
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:06,800
