121
00:06:06,800 --> 00:06:07,280
Sure.

122
00:06:07,440 --> 00:06:08,080
Thank you.

123
00:06:09,320 --> 00:06:10,520
Turn left at the door.

124
00:06:11,080 --> 00:06:11,880
Thank you for your help.

125
00:06:11,880 --> 00:06:12,880
I'm sorry, Ms. Xu.

126
00:06:16,880 --> 00:06:18,480
Have something sweet first.

127
00:06:19,080 --> 00:06:20,440
It helps relieve anxiety.

128
00:06:20,440 --> 00:06:22,920
I didn't bring much with me this time,

129
00:06:22,920 --> 00:06:25,120
