131
00:06:29,920 --> 00:06:33,600
Let's just talk about what kind of person Teacher Liang was.

132
00:06:33,720 --> 00:06:35,200
I watched the security footage.

133
00:06:35,200 --> 00:06:36,600
When she entered the classroom,

134
00:06:36,600 --> 00:06:37,800
