161
00:07:48,280 --> 00:07:49,920
But her temper...

162
00:07:52,560 --> 00:07:54,280
Officers, you can ask around.

163
00:07:54,280 --> 00:07:55,159
In our school,

164
00:07:55,159 --> 00:07:57,320
which young teacher hasn't been scolded by her?

165
00:07:57,320 --> 00:08:00,720
She was always flaunting her seniority and giving attitude.

166
00:08:01,080 --> 00:08:01,810
Captain Luo.

167
00:08:03,320 --> 00:08:04,880
Not much useful information.

168
00:08:04,880 --> 00:08:07,010
We haven't made much progress either.

169
00:08:07,200 --> 00:08:08,320
This Liang Ruqing...

170
00:08:08,320 --> 00:08:10,250
Had conflicts with many teachers,

171
00:08:10,320 --> 00:08:12,050
but they all reconciled later.

172
00:08:12,160 --> 00:08:12,880
Not enough motive.

173
00:08:12,880 --> 00:08:14,560
We haven't finished our interviews yet.

174
00:08:14,560 --> 00:08:16,160
Do you want to meet up with us?

175
00:08:17,160 --> 00:08:19,490
I want to check out Liang Ruqing's office.

176
00:08:20,360 --> 00:08:22,400
This is Mr. Liang's desk.

177
00:08:30,760 --> 00:08:33,600
Has this photo always been on her desk?

178
00:08:33,720 --> 00:08:35,720
It should be newly changed this semester.

179
00:08:35,720 --> 00:08:36,280
I remember

180
00:08:36,280 --> 00:08:38,880
