185
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:00,920
Ruqing!

186
00:09:01,160 --> 00:09:02,290
Don't be impulsive.

187
00:09:02,800 --> 00:09:04,080
What's your relationship to the deceased?

188
00:09:04,080 --> 00:09:06,360
Ruqing, Ruqing!

189
00:09:07,040 --> 00:09:08,320
What's wrong with you?

190
00:09:08,560 --> 00:09:11,200
Ruqing, you were fine when you left this morning.

191
00:09:11,200 --> 00:09:11,920
It's okay.

192
00:09:12,160 --> 00:09:13,020
That's enough.

193
00:09:13,440 --> 00:09:14,520
Ruqing.

194
00:09:14,840 --> 00:09:15,920
My condolences.

195
00:09:16,240 --> 00:09:17,320
Ruqing.

196
00:09:26,320 --> 00:09:27,580
My name is Sun Xiangbo.

197
00:09:27,600 --> 00:09:29,600
I'm Liang Ruqing's partner.

198
00:09:29,600 --> 00:09:30,320
Ruqing...

199
00:09:30,960 --> 00:09:33,160
She was fine when she left this morning.

200
00:09:34,720 --> 00:09:37,120
How could she suddenly jump off a building?

201
00:09:38,360 --> 00:09:40,420
How did you determine it was suicide?

202
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:44,080
I've seen the security footage.

203
00:09:44,080 --> 00:09:46,000
Ruqing jumped by herself.

204
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:47,800
If it's not suicide, then what is it?

205
00:09:47,800 --> 00:09:51,000
Did someone say something to upset her?

206
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:53,160
Or was she bullied at school?

207
00:09:54,560 --> 00:09:56,320
The school must be held responsible.

208
00:09:56,320 --> 00:09:57,720
The school must take full responsibility.

209
00:09:57,720 --> 00:09:59,250
Alright, please calm down.

210
00:09:59,720 --> 00:10:01,850
We need to verify your identity first.

211
00:10:14,880 --> 00:10:16,440
Has the body been identified?

212
00:10:16,440 --> 00:10:17,440
I didn't allow it.

213
00:10:17,440 --> 00:10:19,100
He was too emotional earlier.

214
00:10:21,000 --> 00:10:21,800
Mr. Sun.

215
00:10:23,360 --> 00:10:24,220
It's like this.

216
00:10:24,240 --> 00:10:25,800
Regarding Liang Ruqing's falling case,

217
00:10:25,800 --> 00:10:27,640
we haven't reached a conclusion yet.

218
00:10:27,640 --> 00:10:29,360
But the police will further verify the facts.

219
00:10:29,360 --> 00:10:30,560
If there are any detailed findings,

220
00:10:30,560 --> 00:10:32,080
we'll definitely let you know.

221
00:10:32,080 --> 00:10:32,880
But now,

222
00:10:33,400 --> 00:10:35,660
please come with us to identify the body.

223
00:10:37,520 --> 00:10:37,850
Okay.

224
00:10:45,640 --> 00:10:47,370
This is his basic information.

225
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:50,560
Jue.

226
00:11:01,160 --> 00:11:02,420
Let's go through this.

227
00:11:03,920 --> 00:11:04,980
Let me speak first.

228
00:11:05,600 --> 00:11:07,120
I believe the cause of Liang Ruqing's death

229
00:11:07,120 --> 00:11:09,560
was a carefully planned hypnotic murder.

230
00:11:14,760 --> 00:11:15,480
Why?

231
00:11:17,240 --> 00:11:18,400
Everyone has seen the surveillance footage.

232
00:11:18,400 --> 00:11:19,960
I think everyone can see

233
00:11:19,960 --> 00:11:22,880
her behavior in the footage was very abnormal.

234
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:24,820
According to our autopsy report,

235
00:11:25,400 --> 00:11:28,160
Liang Ruqing died from severe head trauma.

236
00:11:28,360 --> 00:11:30,520
But her limbs had no fractures,

237
00:11:30,520 --> 00:11:33,120
which is inconsistent with typical falling deaths.

238
00:11:33,120 --> 00:11:35,400
Because whether suicide or homicide,

239
00:11:35,560 --> 00:11:37,520
as long as the person is conscious,

240
00:11:37,560 --> 00:11:39,400
at the moment they hit the ground,

241
00:11:39,400 --> 00:11:41,720
they would instinctively use their limbs to brace against impact,

242
00:11:41,720 --> 00:11:43,120
resulting in fractures.

243
00:11:43,360 --> 00:11:44,760
Liang Ruqing didn't have any.

244
00:11:44,760 --> 00:11:46,000
What does this indicate?

245
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:49,320
It shows Liang Ruqing was unconscious when she fell.

246
00:11:49,720 --> 00:11:51,160
Additionally, hypnosis

247
00:11:51,160 --> 00:11:52,720
requires a hypnotist.

248
00:12:05,760 --> 00:12:09,800
Hypnosis requires long-term contact between the hypnotist and subject.

249
00:12:09,800 --> 00:12:10,920
Close contact.

250
00:12:11,960 --> 00:12:13,760
But our investigation revealed

251
00:12:13,800 --> 00:12:14,960
Liang Ruqing's relationships with students

252
00:12:14,960 --> 00:12:16,600
and colleagues were all quite ordinary,

253
00:12:16,600 --> 00:12:18,200
and she had no close friends.

254
00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:20,760
So who could have had close, prolonged contact with her?

255
00:12:20,760 --> 00:12:22,490
Only her husband, Sun Xiangbo.

256
00:12:23,080 --> 00:12:25,800
According to feedback from some teachers at the school,

257
00:12:25,800 --> 00:12:27,080
their marriage

258
00:12:27,080 --> 00:12:28,440
did have some issues.

259
00:12:29,080 --> 00:12:30,600
They argued frequently,

260
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:33,160
but everyone thought highly of Sun Xiangbo.

261
00:12:33,560 --> 00:12:35,360
Looking at all this information,

262
00:12:35,360 --> 00:12:37,640
it's possible that Liang Ruqing

263
00:12:37,640 --> 00:12:38,560
was the one with bigger issues in the marriage.

264
00:12:38,560 --> 00:12:40,480
A model husband in public,

265
00:12:40,880 --> 00:12:43,720
yet with widely known marital problems.

266
00:12:44,080 --> 00:12:45,610
Quite the devoted husband.

267
00:12:46,000 --> 00:12:47,600
Today he made sure everyone saw his

268
00:12:47,600 --> 00:12:48,800
overwhelming grief.

269
00:12:49,440 --> 00:12:51,300
Don't you think he's overacting?

270
00:12:53,560 --> 00:12:56,120
This guy is highly suspicious right now.

271
00:13:02,440 --> 00:13:03,080
Alright.

272
00:13:03,600 --> 00:13:04,840
Everyone go home and get some rest.

273
00:13:04,840 --> 00:13:05,640
Do more research.

274
00:13:05,640 --> 00:13:06,800
Don't just sit around.

275
00:13:06,800 --> 00:13:09,200
Tomorrow we'll visit Sun Xiangbo's place.

276
00:13:15,320 --> 00:13:16,120
Chi Xia.

277
00:13:17,360 --> 00:13:18,560
Are you feeling unwell?

278
00:13:18,560 --> 00:13:19,820
Should I take you home?

279
00:13:19,920 --> 00:13:20,720
No.

280
00:13:21,720 --> 00:13:22,920
Don't worry, Captain Luo.

281
00:13:22,920 --> 00:13:24,720
I won't delay our work progress.

282
00:13:53,920 --> 00:13:55,250
You need to take a break.

