Although it feels good,

285
00:13:59,240 --> 00:14:01,370
getting injured would not be worth it.

286
00:14:02,800 --> 00:14:03,720
In my opinion,

287
00:14:04,360 --> 00:14:08,090
physical pain is ten thousand times better than mental suffering.

288
00:14:09,360 --> 00:14:10,600
But in my view,

289
00:14:11,640 --> 00:14:12,600
physical pain

290
00:14:12,600 --> 00:14:14,730
doesn't eliminate mental suffering.

291
00:14:15,080 --> 00:14:17,880
You might end up suffering twice as much instead.

292
00:14:20,920 --> 00:14:21,720
Ade.

293
00:14:29,760 --> 00:14:30,620
How about this.

294
00:14:31,360 --> 00:14:33,560
Don't just take it out on the punching bag alone.

295
00:14:33,560 --> 00:14:35,560
I'm free today, I can train with you.

296
00:14:36,360 --> 00:14:38,560
This will also reduce your chance of getting hurt.

297
00:14:38,560 --> 00:14:40,240
The gym owner himself is stepping in.

298
00:14:40,240 --> 00:14:42,560
You treat your members quite well.

299
00:14:43,760 --> 00:14:45,420
Alright, no need to be polite.

300
00:14:45,600 --> 00:14:46,040
Give me a moment.

301
00:14:46,040 --> 00:14:46,720
Okay.

302
00:15:23,440 --> 00:15:24,320
You win.

303
00:15:24,320 --> 00:15:26,520
Let's call it a day.

304
00:15:27,360 --> 00:15:29,640
How are you feeling? Any better?

305
00:15:31,360 --> 00:15:32,320
Much better.

306
00:15:34,720 --> 00:15:36,720
If you need this kind of thing again,

307
00:15:36,800 --> 00:15:38,000
just call me anytime.

308
00:15:39,600 --> 00:15:41,530
I'll treat you to dinner sometime.

309
00:15:52,920 --> 00:15:54,880
I've received another complaint letter.

310
00:15:54,880 --> 00:15:55,760
The student witness

311
00:15:55,760 --> 00:15:59,200
didn't cooperate promptly with police to reconstruct the scene.

312
00:15:59,200 --> 00:16:00,600
It's because they said

313
00:16:00,800 --> 00:16:02,600
some officers don't look like police

314
00:16:02,600 --> 00:16:03,520
but like thugs.

315
00:16:04,600 --> 00:16:05,720
They were scared,

316
00:16:05,720 --> 00:16:06,780
do you understand?

317
00:16:07,520 --> 00:16:09,040
How many times have I told you?

318
00:16:09,040 --> 00:16:10,440
Look at that messy hair of yours.

319
00:16:10,440 --> 00:16:12,360
I've told you to pay attention to your appearance

320
00:16:12,360 --> 00:16:13,400
and your image.

321
00:16:13,640 --> 00:16:14,560
Do you know how

322
00:16:15,480 --> 00:16:16,720
terrible this influence is?

323
00:16:16,720 --> 00:16:17,720
My hairstyle has nothing to do with solving cases.

324
00:16:17,720 --> 00:16:21,250
You've got a hundred comebacks for everything I say, don't you?

325
00:16:22,000 --> 00:16:24,860
Do you want to keep fighting with yourself forever?

326
00:16:39,720 --> 00:16:41,080
This is way too short.

327
00:16:41,360 --> 00:16:43,690
Listen to me. Short hair looks energetic.

328
00:16:43,920 --> 00:16:45,440
You're a police officer now.

329
00:16:45,440 --> 00:16:47,920
You need to present a good image to the public.

330
00:16:47,920 --> 00:16:48,880
It's all because of this injury.

331
00:16:48,880 --> 00:16:50,810
I missed your induction ceremony.

332
00:16:51,120 --> 00:16:52,640
Let's make up for it at home.

333
00:16:52,640 --> 00:16:53,200
Come on.

334
00:16:53,200 --> 00:16:53,840
Sis.

335
00:16:54,360 --> 00:16:56,400
Is your hand really okay for this?

336
00:16:56,400 --> 00:16:57,860
Maybe we should forget it.

337
00:16:57,920 --> 00:17:00,000
Don't make a fuss about this little injury.

338
00:17:00,000 --> 00:17:00,930
Stand straight.

339
00:17:06,400 --> 00:17:08,040
Is this okay?

340
00:17:08,040 --> 00:17:08,900
Yes, it's fine.

341
00:17:09,920 --> 00:17:11,250
You look very handsome.

342
00:17:12,920 --> 00:17:16,000
When I'm on the front lines in our unit,

343
00:17:16,000 --> 00:17:16,930
let me handle it.

344
00:17:17,520 --> 00:17:19,180
I won't let you get hurt again.

345
00:17:19,359 --> 00:17:21,800
Would a delicate flower choose to join the major crimes unit?

346
00:17:21,800 --> 00:17:23,359
If you actually encounter a case,

347
00:17:23,359 --> 00:17:26,000
your duty is to protect the safety of the people.

348
00:17:26,000 --> 00:17:28,240
Don't always worry about your big sister.

349
00:17:28,240 --> 00:17:29,760
That's Officer Luo for you.

350
00:17:29,760 --> 00:17:31,320
Your sense of duty is deeper than mine.

351
00:17:31,320 --> 00:17:32,560
I need to learn from you.

352
00:17:32,560 --> 00:17:33,320
At ease.

353
00:17:35,000 --> 00:17:35,800
Attention!

354
00:17:51,360 --> 00:17:52,120
Sis.

355
00:17:53,880 --> 00:17:54,940
I'll listen to you.

356
00:18:08,440 --> 00:18:09,240
Young Master.

357
00:18:10,440 --> 00:18:13,900
It's not easy to fight when you're deliberately holding back.

358
00:18:16,600 --> 00:18:19,400
Her fighting skills are much sharper than before.

359
00:18:19,400 --> 00:18:20,660
She must join the game.

360
00:18:21,800 --> 00:18:22,800
She has no choice.

361
00:19:05,160 --> 00:19:07,200
His place is too clean.

362
00:19:07,280 --> 00:19:08,960
It's so clean as if he knew we were coming

363
00:19:08,960 --> 00:19:10,360
and tidied up specially.

364
00:19:10,440 --> 00:19:12,240
In the relationship between Liang Ruqing and Sun Xiangbo,

365
00:19:12,240 --> 00:19:13,760
there's a third person involved.

366
00:19:13,760 --> 00:19:16,080
Damn it. He just can't stand seeing me do well.

367
00:19:16,080 --> 00:19:17,160
She deserves to die.
